VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'don\'t want to necessarily say this was buried, but in the announcement, Adobe didn\'t also mention VEO 2. And that is kind of the odd man out here, you know, considering that everything else is an image generator. I did forget to mention'

[03:27] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'that they also did bring up Fall to use as an upscaler. But, as most of you know, VEO 2 is Google\'s video generator. So, it\'s a it\'s a little bit out of place here. But, that is interesting as it does very much echo back to Adobe\'s'

[03:40] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'announcement last year that Sora would be incorporated into Adobe Premiere kind of as a clip extension function. Now, obviously, that never happened and, you know, obviously, given the state of Sora'

