VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'builder over here. And just to show you how easy all of this is, as I famously say on the channel quite often, only psychopaths use light mode. So, I\'m going to give it a prompt of create a'

[06:53] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'toggle switch for a dark mode and then another mode for a darker mode. So, it actually ended up going and one-upping me with a triple mode toggle switch of light, dark, and darker. I suppose we do have to let the psychopaths use our web'

